    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>gram flour</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> in a separate bowl with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cayenne</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>gram flour mix</strong></p><p>Reserve 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> of <strong>gram flour mix</strong>, then add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>gram flour mix</strong> with the <strong>marinated tofu</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>coated tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
