    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated tofu</strong> to the pan and cook for 6-8 min or until the tofu is crispy and golden – this is your<strong> crispy tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
