      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>coriander</strong>, including the stalks</p><p>Roll your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
