      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and the <strong>reserved gram flour mix </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[900ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
