        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and the<strong> remaining soy sauce </strong>to the pot with<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Whisk everything together until there are no lumps – this is your <strong>coconut broth</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
