            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fine egg noodles</strong> and<strong> mooli slaw mix</strong> to the <strong>coconut broth</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 1-2 min further or until the noodles are tender</p><p>Once tender, add the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and stir it all together – these are your <strong>Burmese-style coconut noodles</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
