    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Burmese-style coconut noodles </strong>in a bowl and top with the <strong>crispy tofu </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
